## Routing

```
/splash                     SplashPage (sets sessionStorage hopahopa_splash_shown)
/welcome                    WelcomePage (sets localStorage hopahopa_welcome_seen)
'' (root, splashGuard)
  map                       MapPage        (tab)
  stats                     StatsPage      (tab)
  settings                  SettingsPage   (tab)
  country/:code             CountryDetailPage
  ''                        → redirect to map
```

`splashGuard` is an inline guard in `app.routes.ts`; it redirects to `/splash` if `hopahopa_splash_shown` is not `'true'` in `sessionStorage`.

> **Note:** First-run logic is handled entirely inside `SplashPage`. The `welcome.guard.ts` file has been deleted (it was dead code).

## Services

| Service | File | Responsibility |
|---|---|---|
| `CountryService` | `services/country.service.ts` | Source of truth for all ~195 countries; Angular **signals + computed** for counts; load/merge from storage; toggle visited; update stats/cities/notes; auto-save via `effect()` |
| `StorageService` | `services/storage.service.ts` | **Capacitor Preferences** key `travelmap_countries`; generic JSON get/set/remove; migration from legacy localStorage; optional IndexedDB `HopaHopaDB` cleanup |
| `AchievementService` | `services/achievement.service.ts` | Milestone / continent / special achievements; sync unlock state with `CountryService`; celebrations (sound, haptics, modal); persists to `localStorage` key `hopahopa_achievements` |
| `SettingsService` | `services/settings.service.ts` | Forces dark mode on `documentElement` / `body`; `resetSettings()` removes preferences key |
| `OverlayService` | `services/overlay.service.ts` | On `NavigationStart`, dismisses modals, popovers, alerts, action sheets; initialized from `AppComponent` |
| `PageTransitionService` | `services/page-transition.service.ts` | Shared state (position, country id/name) for map → country-detail transition animation |
| `ErrorService` | `services/error.service.ts` | User-facing toasts/alerts for categorized errors; logging helper |
| `CitySearchService` | `services/city-search.service.ts` | Wraps Mapbox Geocoding API (`/geocoding/v5/mapbox.places`) to return city suggestions filtered by country ISO code; used by `CountryDetailPage` autocomplete |

## Shared components

| Component | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `AnimatedBackgroundComponent` | Decorative background used on several pages |
| `AchievementModalComponent` | Celebration modal (lazy-imported by `AchievementService`) |
| `CircularMenuComponent` | Long-press radial menu on the map |
| `CountryPreviewCardComponent` | Hover/tap preview card on map |

**Directive:** `ButtonPressDirective` (`appButtonPress`) — press animation + Capacitor haptics.

## Domain models (`src/app/models/country.model.ts`)

```typescript
interface Country {
  code: string;       // ISO alpha-2
  name: string;
  visited: boolean;
  photoIds: string[];
  visitCount?: number;
  daysStayed?: number;
  cities?: string[];
  cityCoordinates?: Record<string, [number, number]>; // city name → [lng, lat] for map pins
  note?: string;      // max 120 chars enforced in CountryService
}
```

Other types: `Achievement`, `UnlockedAchievement`, `AchievementCategory` (in `AchievementService`); `TransitionState` (in `PageTransitionService`); `AppSettings` (in `SettingsService`); `ErrorContext` / `ErrorType` (in `ErrorService`).

## Storage keys

| Key | Storage | Content |
|---|---|---|
| `travelmap_countries` | Capacitor Preferences | Serialized country array |
| `hopahopa_achievements` | `localStorage` | Unlocked achievement IDs |
| `hopahopa_welcome_seen` | `localStorage` | `'true'` after onboarding |
| `hopahopa_splash_shown` | `sessionStorage` | `'true'` per session |

## External APIs

- **Mapbox:** map tiles + dark style (`mapbox://styles/mapbox/dark-v11`); token from `environment.mapboxToken`
- **GeoJSON (countries):** `https://raw.githubusercontent.com/datasets/geo-countries/master/data/countries.geojson` with fallback to `assets/countries.geojson`
- **No custom REST backend** — fully offline-first; all data lives on-device

## Capacitor plugins in use

`@capacitor/app`, `@capacitor/camera`, `@capacitor/filesystem`, `@capacitor/haptics`, `@capacitor/keyboard`, `@capacitor/preferences`, `@capacitor/share`, `@capacitor/splash-screen`, `@capacitor/status-bar`

## Known caveats / tech debt

- `StorageService.loadCountries()` currently maps only `code`, `name`, `visited`, `photoIds` — `visitCount`, `daysStayed`, `cities`, `note` may not survive a full reload
- `src/environments/environment.ts` is gitignored (developer local copy); copy from `environment.example.ts` and fill in your Mapbox token for local dev
- The pre-existing `Cannot find module '../../environments/environment'` lint error in `map.page.ts` is expected in CI/readonly environments where `environment.ts` is absent
